Visit your favorite FLAPS and buy a back of the oil absorbent. Basically a 
fancy version of kitty litter but it doesn't get so mushy like the kitty 
litter I've used in the past.

Sprinkle it out, and leave it. Walk or work on it. In a few days sweep it up.

